Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.29,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提煉純度的問題還是沒有解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.43,0:02:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上結晶方向還是不够一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這也已經超過標準了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以這裏的設備來說 這已經是極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.74,0:02:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們“馬克思”的商品比正規品還要高級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容許出現任何暇疵品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重做！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.21,0:02:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？ 有人來搜查？ 難道是GOTT？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是GOTT的强制搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.45,0:02:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們涉嫌重力控制媒介“Hi-G”的非法製造及販賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.33,0:02:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是GOTT的ES成員Alv（注：Elf）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dvergr（注：Dwarf）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開槍！開槍！你們在幹什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二話 重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那件案子的沒收品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就“Hi-G”來說這個容器還真大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，要小心點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忌妒是很難看的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然同樣是ES成員 但她們是S級的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.17,0:04:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等級比我們還高很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.11,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是忌妒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看不慣她們的態度而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有可以相提幷論的實力的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會有厭惡的感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是空的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，報告上說的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封裝方面也沒有任何异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲東擊西…？ 陷阱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們居然被設計了…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.31,0:05:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercredi，這件事交給Tweedledee跟Tweedledum
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.68,0:05:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的耻辱希望能由我們自己來彌補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.98,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽就爲你們準備支援人員吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶Eclair、Lumiere去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，也請Armbrust監察官過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙子星Latium及Latinus
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.68,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人工收容所Globe Cage\N就圍繞著它的極限軌道運行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經確認過身份的馬克思成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被收容于此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.62,0:05:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用爲了取證而特地跑到那種地方吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有拜讬你一起過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是局長的命令我才不來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有說些什麽吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.08,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麽靠近的極限軌道上居然還沒有被溶化掉耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.12,0:06:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都有賴于超過正常30倍的重力緩衝控制系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果控制系統完蛋的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收容所當場變成火葬場？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可真是服務周到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我留在這裏等你們好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船的自動誘導系統雖然正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但通常應該會有獄警來負責控制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們吃完午飯之後又睡個午覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在期待什麽啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.34,0:07:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不過來的話就把你們丟在這裏了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我們行動是你的工作耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨你高興好了，怠忽職守監察官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個打掃機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Hi-G”的箱子空了之後\N緊接著是空蕩蕩的收容所？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是低劣的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，尸體有那麽稀奇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是重力炸彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alv，用反射裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.09,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，就只會耍些騙小孩的把戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.19,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，應該逮捕的活證人都已經被滅口了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情結束了，打道回府吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.57,0:09:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，舉手之勞幫個忙也好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.07,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔？ 沒聽說過有哪個ES成員會爲了這種事情求救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里…那個重力炸彈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,物理防禦盾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多保重了，小姐們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.93,0:10:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事…我剛剛…找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但搞不好太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，終于停下來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.05,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要崩潰了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在內部使用了兩次重力炸彈那是當然的羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史瓦爾多…我們的船不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去！那個傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.37,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊，已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.52,0:11:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，總算來得…啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來，這個地方已經變得相當脆弱了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子…要優雅一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船想去救她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La Muse！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它來救我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armbrust他…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.55,0:13:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪走“Hi-G”、還有我們的船的全都是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…那個渾蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還有留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒打開來看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.83,0:13:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用看也知道內容…對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麽一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要念了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然選這種地方當交易場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你對古典的東西還蠻有興趣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是行星聯合的官員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是守時啊，雜耍師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.14,0:14:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的匿稱是“Magician”（注：魔術師）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.61,0:14:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不好吧，是立體影像嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.34,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上只有“小心”才是長壽的秘訣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“馬克思”那夥人就連這點也不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然那個重力炸彈是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是商品測試啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力炸彈加上重力地雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我們“休巴”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有原料的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論多少都可以生産出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是“Hi-G”吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.78,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，似乎是真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.61,0:15:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在非活性狀態下重力偏差值0.2嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是上等貨，而且量也很够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來似乎很合您的胃口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.46,0:15:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有考慮過放弃製造武器改製造人工重力系統呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這玩笑真是有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有比武器更值錢的商品的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就教教我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高額的利潤伴隨而來的就是高度的風險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學校難道沒有學過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道是這麽一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.68,0:15:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謊言跟背叛或許是你最厲害的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我已經受够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手脚還真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經請“她”好好保護你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.90,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀…還真像是VIP級的待遇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意設下陷阱的嗎？ 雜耍的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donnersclac 那個詐欺犯就交給你羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是“Magician”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧！只能撑住一發而已嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很危險呢，Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，被防禦盾干擾到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以GOTT直屬ES成員的權力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.79,0:18:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指控你們爲星際罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.03,0:18:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長，我要申請逮捕執行權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.83,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,申請核准，Eclair、Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.41,0:18:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕？太愚蠢了 難道你們想逮捕立體影像嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，你還沒發現嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，辛苦你們誘敵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長，緊接著“馬克思”之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“休巴”的據點也瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，Alv、Dvergr
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們以爲我會這麽簡單的束手就擒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力炸彈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次你們躲不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.19,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere只要在可以接近目標的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.16,0:19:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以强制奪取操縱系統的控制權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何况是這麽近的距離…對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很堅固的箱子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我最自傲的好東西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，却讓你把它弄壞了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過"這是我最自傲的好東西"嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個老是抓不到的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉由老兄你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算把兩方面的人馬都掃除殆盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麽樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“馬克思”或是“休巴”早晚都會自已垮掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.51,0:20:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要讓那群傢伙繼續胡作非爲下去那我可受不了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這區域內28個殖民地的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.27,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這麽說的話會不會成爲笑柄呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愛裝模作樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低著床率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生後的畸形比率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及免疫系統功能降低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏的低重力條件下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對寶寶而言絕對不是個好環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我們是聽說了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…這是真的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個殖民地也終于有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家期盼了好久的“人工重力調整室”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…\N瑪莉亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.94,0:21:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們可以像在地球一樣生育孩子了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快出發到下個殖民地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.99,0:21:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
